This package ports and adapts the HTTP-402 "Payment" (draft-httpauth-payment /
MPP) protocol layer from @getalby/lightning-tools (src/402/), which is:

  Copyright (c) 2023 Alby contributors <hello@getalby.com> (https://getalby.com)

and distributed under the MIT License. The header-parse, base64url, JCS
(RFC 8785) canonicalization, challenge-echo, and single-retry control flow are
derived from that work. See src/envelope.ts and src/mpp.ts for in-file
attribution. The original MIT terms below cover the ported portions.

